title: 2016 Week 8 review
itunes:title: 2016 Week 8 review
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, and Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game breaking down each Week 8 matchup which included a shootout in Atlanta between the Packers and the Falcons, and an overtime showdown between the league’s best rookie QBs.
